#

Spicy Mango Glazed Salmon

$22.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodAmericanDinnerGrilled

Description

A vibrant and zesty dish combining succulent salmon with a sweet and spicy mango glaze, served with a side of asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Mango: 1, ripe
  • Soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Honey: 1 tbsp
  • Lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • Chili flakes: 1 tsp
  • Asparagus: 1 lb
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
